Sravanthi Agrees to Borrow 6.3 Billion Rupees in 10-Year Loan

-- B y   A n u r a g   J o s h i
-- 
2011-03-25T04:45:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/sravanthi-agrees-to-borrow-6-3-billion-rupees-in-10-year-loan.html
Sravanthi Energy Pvt., the Gurgaon-
based power group, agreed to borrow 6.3 billion rupees ($141
million) via a syndicated loan.  The company signed a 10-year facility with lenders,
according to Chief Executive Officer Vijay Gupta in a telephone
interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anurag Joshi in Mumbai at 
 ajoshi53@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will McSheehy at 
 wmcsheehy@bloomberg.net . 